    </div>

    <div class="card-header">
      <h2 class="header-two">STEP TWO</h2>
      <h3 class="header-three">Accept bids from pros</h3>
      <p>You will need to give a description of your event and put out the jobs that you need!</p>
    </div>

    <div class="card-header">
      <h2 class="header-two">STEP THREE</h2>
      <h3 class="header-three">Enjoy your event</h3>
      <p>You will need to give a description of your event and put out the jobs that you need!</p>
    </div>
  </div>

</div>
<%= render 'shared/footer' %>


  <div class="long-button">
    <span>Are you a professional looking for work near you?</span>
    <%= link_to events_path do %>
    <button class="button long-button-button">Start here</button>
    <% end %>
  </div>
</div>
